    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Golf-Like</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Golf-Like</strong> 是一款基于技巧的游戏，将高尔夫的核心逻辑带入一个极简而抽象的游戏空间。<br>每个关卡都考验玩家对角度、力量和时机的把握。没有多余的元素——只有控制、物理和结果。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292300/extras/62dcbc9885eb96d232f719d8240596de.avif?t=1772455656\" width=1500 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏目前正在开发中。内容和细节可能会随时间变化。最终目标是提供纯粹的游戏体验和高度的重玩价值。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292300/extras/d84e94a8a657db69d1d7de3ae435f1b6.avif?t=1772455656\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292300/extras_big/d84e94a8a657db69d1d7de3ae435f1b6.avif?t=1772455656 width=1560 height=504 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
